shingle slip
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a steep slide of running scree or loose stones [usually on high mountain or hill country. ]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
